hadiths[92]{hadithnumber,text}:
4514,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jo bimari utaari hai to uski shifa bhi utaari hai.'' Bukhari ."
4515,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her bimari ke liye dawaai hai, jab dawaai bimari ke muwaafiq ho jati hai to mareez Allah ke hukm se sehat yaab ho jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4516,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shifa teen chizon mein hai : pachhney lagwaaney mein ya shehad peeney mein ya aag se daaghney sey, aur main apni ummat ko daaghney se mana karta hun.'' Bukhari ."
4517,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwa ehzaab ( khandaq (ke moqe par Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko gardan ki rag mein teer laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen dagh diya. rawahu Muslim ."
4518,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko gardan ki rag mein teer laga to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney dast Mubarak se teer ke paikaan ke sath usey dagh diya, phir is par waram aa gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dusri martaba usey dagh diya. rawahu Muslim ."
4519,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik tabeeb bheja to usney unki eik rag kaat di phir usko dagh diya. rawahu Muslim."
4520,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kalonji mein maut ke siwa her bimari se shifa hai.'' ibne-Shahab ne farmaya : ( السام ( se murad maut aur (al-abbatus-sodaa) se kalonji murad hai. muttafaq aleh.
4521,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur usney arz kya, merey bhai ko pechish lagi hui hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey shehad pilaao.'' usney usey shehad pilaya , wo phir aaya aur arz kya : maine usey shehad pilaya magar us se pechish aur bhi ziyada ho gaee hai, aapney teen martaba usey aisey hi farmaya , phir wo chauthi martaba aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( yehi ( farmaya : ''usey shehad pilaao.'' usney arz kya, main usey pila chuka hun lekin uski pechish mein izafa hi hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka farman sacha hai jabkey terey bhai ke pet ki ghalati hai.'' usney phir pilaya to wo sehat yaab ho gaya. muttafaq aleh."
4522,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' seengi lagwaana aur qust bahri ka istimal behtareen tariqa ilaj hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4523,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''azra (eik waram hai jo bache ke halaq mein kasrat khoon ki wajeh se ho jata hai) ki wajeh se apney bachon ke galey daba kar unhen takleef na paunchaao, balke tum qust istemal karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4524,"Hazrat umme-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum us halaq ke waram ki wajeh se apni aulad ka halaq kyon dabaati ho? bas tum ye aud hindi istimal karo, kyonkey is mein saat bimariyon se shifa hai, un mein se eik nimooniya hai, halaq ke waram ki wajeh se usey naak se dala jaey aur nimooniya ki surat mein munh ke eik taraf se dali jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4525,"Hazrat Aaisha aur Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bukhaar jahannam ki bhap se hai, tum usey pani ke sath thanda karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4526,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nazar lag janey, dank mein aur namla bimari ( pasli mein daney nikal aatey hain aur zakhm pad jatey hain ( ki surat mein dam karney ki rukhsat inayat farmaai hai. rawahu Muslim ."
4527,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nazar lag janey ki surat mein dam karaney ka hukm farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4528,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey ghar main eik ladki dekhi jiskey chehrey par zardi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dam karaao kyonkey usey nazar lagi hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4529,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dam se mana farma diya to, aale-Amr bin hazam aaye aur unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! hamarey paas dam tha jo ham bichhu ke das leney par kya kartey they, aur aapney us se mana farma diya hai, unhoney wo dam aap ko sunaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main is mein koi harj nahin samajhta, tum mein se jo shakhs apney bhai ko faeyda pahuncha sakta hai to wo usey faeyda pahunchaey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4530,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham daure-jahiliyat mein dam kya kartey they, ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aap is barey mein kya farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney dam mujhey sunaao, aisa dam jis mein shirk na ho, is mein koi harj nahin .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4531,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nazar ( ki taaseer) Sabit hai, agar koi chiz taqdir par sabqat ley janey wali hoti to nazar is par sabqat ley jati aur jab tum se ghusl ka mutalba kya jaey to ghusl karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4532,"Hazrat Usama bin Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham ilaj muaalija keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, Allah ke bando! ilaj muaalija karo kyonkey Allah ne budhapey ke siwa aisi koi bimari paida nahin ki jis ke liye shifa paida na ki ho.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4533,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney bimaron ko khaney par majbur na kya karo, kyonkey Allah Taala unhen khilata pilata hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4534,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Asad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) ko shooka (ye surkh baada hai jo ghalba khoon se paida hota hai) ki bimari mein dagh diya. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4535,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm farmaya ke ham qust bahri aur zaitun se nimooniya ka ilaj karen. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4536,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nimoniya ke ilaj ke liye zaitun aur waras ( buti ( ki tareef kya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4537,"Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se daryaft kya, tum julab ke liye konsi dawa istemal karti ho? maine arz kya : shabram (chuney ki tarah eik dana hai jo ke bahut garm hai, uska pani dawa ke taur par peetey hain (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo to intehai garm hai.'' wo bayan karti hain, phir main sana ke sath julab leti . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar kisi chiz mein maut ki shifa hoti to wo sana mein hoti .'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4538,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne bimari utaari hai to usney dawaai bhi utaari hai aur usney her bimari ke liye dawaai banai hai, tum ilaj muaalija karo aur haram chiz ke sath ilaj muaalija mat karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4539,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haram chiz ko bator dawa istimal karney se bhi mana farmaya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4540,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khaadima Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jis shakhs ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se dard sar ki shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yehi farmaya ke '' pachhney lagaao .'' aur jisney apney paaon mein takleef ka zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' mehndi lagaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4541,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khaadima Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko talwaar waghera ya kisi aur tarah koi bhi zakhm aa jata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey is par mahndi laganey ka hukm farmatey. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4542,Hazrat abu Kabsha Anmari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar aur apney kandhon ke darmiyan pachhney lagwaaya kartey they aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''jo shakhs us khoon mein se kuch khoon nikalwata hai to agar wo kisi marz ka kisi dawaai ke zariey ilaj na bhi karey to uskey liye kuch Muzir nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja .
4543,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne moch ke dard ki wajeh se apni raan ke ooper pachhney lagwaaey . rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4544,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shabe-Mairaj ke mutalliq hadees bayan farmaai ke wo farishton ki jis bhi jamaat ke paas se guzrey to wo yehi kehtey ke ''apni ummat ko pachhney lagwaaney ka hukm farmaeyn.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4545,Hazrat Abdurreman bin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik tabeeb ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maindak ko dawaai mein dalney ke mutalliq puchha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey uskey qatl karney se mana farma diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4546,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) gardan ki dono ragon aur kandhon ke darmiyan pachhney lagwaaya kartey they. Abu-Dawud, Imam Tirmizi aur Imam ibne-Maja ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( chaand ki) satrah , Unais aur ikkees taareekh ko pachhney lagwaaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4547,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (chaand ki) sattarah, Unais aur ikkees taareekh ko pachhney lagana pasand farmatey they. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
4548,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs (chaand ki) sattarah, Unais aur ikkis taareekh ko pachhney lagwaaey wo her bimari se mehfooz rahega .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4549,"Hazrat Kabsha binte-abi bakra se riwayat hai ke uskey walid mangal ke roz pachhney lagwaaney se apney ehle khana ko mana kya kartey they, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke '' mangal ka din ( ghalba ( khoon ka din hai aur us main eik ghadi hai ke is mein khoon thamta nahin .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4550,"Hazrat Zohri (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kartey hain, ''jo shakhs buddh ya hafte ke din pachhney lagwaaey aur wo baras ka shikar ho jaey to wo us surat mein khud ko hi malamat karey.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, aur Abu-Dawood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye mashhoor hai ke ye riwayat musnad hai, lekin ye sahih nahin. ( rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ( ."
4551,"Hazrat Imam Zohri (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs haftey ya buddh ke roz pachhney lagwaaey ya koi dawaai lep karey to wo baras ka shikar honey ki surat mein sirf apney nafs ko hi malamat karey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4552,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Abdullah ne meri gardan main eik dhaaga dekha to puchha : ye kya hai? maine kaha : merey liye dam kya hua dhaaga hai, unhoney usey pakad kar kaat diya, phir farmaya : tum aale-Abdullah shirk se be niaz ho, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' be-shak dam, taawiz aur jadu shirk hai.'' maine kaha : aap is tarah kyon kehtey hain? meri aankh mein shadeed dard tha main falan Yahudi ke paas jati thi, jab wo dam karta to dard ruk jata tha, (ye sun kar) Abdullah ne farmaya : ye mehaz shetan ka amal hai, wo apna haath aankh par maarta hai. jab dam kya jata hai to wo haath maarna chhod deta hai, tumharey liye itna kehna hi kafi tha jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''logon ke rab! bimari ley ja, aur shifa ata farma, tu hi shifa ata karney wala hai, shifa sirf teri hi hai, aisi shifa ata kar ke wo koi bimari na chhodey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4553,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jadu, mantr (siflii amal ko siflii ilm se door karney (ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shetani amal hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4554,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main kuch farq nahin samajhta ke main tiryaaq piyun ya taawiz latkaaun ya apni taraf se sher kahun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4555,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne dagh lagwaaya ya dam karaya to wo tawakkul se la-talluq ho gaya.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4556,"Hazrat Esa bin Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Abdullah bin Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unhen surkh baada ka marz tha, maine kaha : aap taawiz kyon nahin letey? unhoney kaha : ham us se Allah ki panah chahtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs koi chiz latkaata hai to usey usi ke supurd kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4557,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nazar lag janey ya kisi ke dasney se dam karna jayez hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
4558,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne usey Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja .
4559,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nazar lag janey ya kisi chiz ke das leney ya naksir jari honey par dam karna durust hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4560,"Hazrat Asma bin Umes (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad ko bahut jald nazar lag jati hai, kya main unhen dam karaaun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, kyonkey agar taqdir par koi chiz ghalib hoti to is par nazar ghalib aati.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4561,"Hazrat shifa bint Abdullah bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to main Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum is (Hafsa (Raziallahu anha)) ko namla (phunsiyan jo pasli par nikalti hain) ka dam nahin sikha deti jis tarah tum ne usey likhna sikhaya hai?'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4562,"Hazrat abu-Umama bin Sehal bin Hanif bayan kartey hain, Aamir bin Rabeea ne Sehal bin Hanif ko ghusl kartey huey dekha to unhoney kaha, Allah ki qism ! maine jis qadr safed w mulaaim jild aaj dekhi hai aisi kabhi nahin dekhi, raawi bayan kartey hain, (isi baat par) Sehal be hosh ho kar gir gaey, unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap ko Sehal bin Hanif ke barey mein kuch khabar hai? Allah ki qism ! wo to apna sar bhi nahin uthatey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum uskey mutalliq kisi ke barey mein guman kartey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya, ham Aamir bin Rabeea ke barey mein guman kartey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aamir ko bulaya aur us se sakht lehjey mein baat ki aur farmaya : ''tum apney bhai ko qatl kartey ho, tum ne uskey liye barkat ki dua kyon na ki, uskey liye ghusl karo.'' Aamir ne uskey liye eik bartan mein apna chehra , apney haath , apni kohniyaan , apney ghutney , paaon ke atraaf aur izaar ke sath ke aaza (ang) dhoey, phir wo pani is par dala gaya to wo ( uth kar) logon ke sath chal pada aur usey koi takleef nahin thi. aur Imam Malik ne isey riwayat kya hai, aur unki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' be-shak nazar ( ki taaseer ( Sabit hai, iskey liye wuzu kar.'' usney uskey liye wuzu kya. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w Malik ( ."
4563,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (azkaar ke zariey) jinnon aur insan ki nazar se panah talab kya kartey they yahan tak ke Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas nazil huin , jab wo nazil huin to aapney unhen ley liya aur jo un dono ke ilawa tha usey tarak kar diya. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4564,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya tum mein ''Mugharribun'' dekhey gaey?'' maine arz kya, ''Mugharribun'' kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo log ( jo Allah ka zikr nahin kartey ( un mein jin (shetan ( shareek ho jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4565,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''behtareen ilaj jiskey . . . .'' ( بَابُ التَّرَجُّلِ ( mein zikr ki gaee hai. zaeef taqaddum.
4566,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meda (pet) badan ka hoz hai, jabkey ragein ( her taraf sey) uski taraf aati hain, jab meda durust hoga to ragein tandurusti lekar wapis aati hain, aur jab meda bimar hota hai, to ragein bimari lekar wapis aati hain. mauzu , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4567,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh rahey they aapney apna haath zamin par rakha to bichho ne aap ko das liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna joota maar kar usey maar diya. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to farmaya : ''Allah bichho par lanat farmaai wo kisi namazi ko chhodta hai na kisi aur ko.'' ya farmaya : '' kisi Nabi ko chhodta hai na kisi aur ko.'' phir aapney namak aur pani mangaaya aur unhen eik bartan mein jama kar diya. phir aap us ungli par jahan usney dasaa tha dalney lagey, usey malney lagey aur muawwizatain ke zariey us se panah talab karney lagey. Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein Shobil-emaan mein zikr ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4568,"Hazrat Usman bin Abdullah bin Mohab bayan kartey hain, merey ehle khana ne pani ka piyala de-kar mujhey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja , aur ye dastoor tha ke jab kisi ko nazar lag jati ya koi aur masla darpesh hota to wo pani ka bartan Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhej diya kartey , wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal , jo ke unhoney chaandi ki ghanti mein rakhey huey they, nikaaltiin aur unhen us shakhs ke liye (pani mein) hilaatin aur bimar aadmi wo pani pi leta. raawi bayan kartey hain, maine us dibiya mein jhank kar dekha to maine surkh baal dekhay. Bukhari ."
4569,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se kuch logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya, khumbi zamin ki chechak hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kumbi, man ( man w salwa) ki eik qism hai aur uska pani aankh ke liye shifa ka zaria hai, aur ajwa ( khajoor ( jannat se hai aur wo zahar ka tiryaaq hai.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine teen ya paanch ya saat khunbiyaan leen, unhen nichod kar unke pani ko eik sheeshi mein rakh liya , aur maine apni us londi ki aakhon mein wo pani dala jiski aakhon se pani behta rehta tha, to wo us se sehatyaab ho gaee. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. zaeef rawahu Tirmizi ."
4570,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs her maah teen roz shehad chaat-ta hai to usey koi badi bimari laahiq nahin hoti.'' ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4571,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shifa deney wali do chizon ko lazim pakdo (yani) shehad aur Quran.'' Imam ibne-Maja ne dono riwaayatein naqal ki hain, aur Imam Behaqi ne unhen Shobil-emaan mein naqal kya aur farmaya : sahih baat ye hai ke aakhiri (dusri ( hadees ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf hai. ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4572,"Hazrat abu Kabsha Anmari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zahar wali bakri ( khaney ( ki wajeh se apney sar ke beech mein pachhney lagwaaey. Maamer bayan kartey hain, maine bhi zahar ke asar ke baghair hi apney sar ke beech mein pachhney lagwaaey to mera haafza jata raha yahan tak ke dorane-namaz mujhey Sura Fatiha ka luqma diya jata tha. rawahu rizeen ."
4573,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Naafe ! mera fishaar khoon badh raha hai kisi pachhney laganey waley nojawan ko merey paas laao , dekhna wo boodha ya bacha na ho, raawi bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' khaali pet pachhney lagwaana ziyada behtar hai, wo aql w Faham aur hafzey mein izafa karta hai, jis shakhs ne pachhney lagwaaney hon to wo Jumerat ke roz Allah Taala ka naam lekar pachhney lagwaaey, Juma hafta aur itwaar ko pachhney lagwaaney se bacho. peer aur mangal ko pachhney lagwaao aur buddh ke roz pachhney lagwaaney se bacho, kyonkey ye wo din hai jis roz Ayub (Alaihissalam) aazmaaish ka shikar huye, juzaam aur baras buddh ke roz ya buddh ki raat hi zahir hotey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4574,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qamrii mahiney ki satrah taareekh ko mangal ke din pachhney lagwaana saal bhar ki bimariyon ke liye dawaai hai.'' Imam Ahmed ke shagrid Harab bin-Ismail kirmaani ne usey riwayat kya hai, aur iski sanad qawi nahin, aur muntqa mein isi tarah hai."
4575,rizeen ne iski misl Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu rizeen .
4576,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' badshigooni kuch bhi nahin, aur uski behtar surat faal hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, faal kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achi baat jo tum mein se koi eik sunta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4577,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na koi bimari mutaaddi hai aur na koi badshigooni hai. aur ullu manhoos hai aur na maahe-safar, aur majzoom se aisey bhago jaisey to sher se bhaagta hai.'' Bukhari ."
4578,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' na koi bimari mutaaddi hai aur na ullu manhoos hai aur na hi maah safar .'' ( ye sun kar) eik dehati ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! un oonton ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai jo registaan mein rehtey hain aur wo hiran malum hotey hain, us main eik khaarish zada oont shamil ho jata hai to wo unhen bhi khaarish laga deta hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to phir pehley ( oont ( ko kis ne khaarish zada kya ?'' Bukhari ."
4579,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na koi bimari mutaaddi hai aur na ullu manhoos hai aur na koi sitaara manhoos hai aur na safar manhoos hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4580,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' koi bimari mutaaddi hai na maah safar manhoos hai na koi bhoot hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4581,"Hazrat Amr bin shareed apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : wafad Saqif main eik kodhi shakhs tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski taraf pegham bheja ke '' teri baiat ho gaee hai lihaza tum wapis chaley jaao .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4582,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faal letey they aur aap badshiguni nahin letey they aur aap achey naam pasand kartey they. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4583,"Hazrat qatan bin Qabisa (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''parindon ke zariey faal lena, lakeerein khinch kar faal lena aur badshigooni lena jadu ki iqsaam hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4584,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''badshigoonii lena shirk hai, aapney ye jumla teen martaba farmaya : '' aur ham mein se agar kisi ke dil mein ye khayal aata hai to Allah tawakkul ke zariey usey khatam kar deta hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : maine Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bayan kartey huey suna : Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab is hadees ke mutalliq kaha kartey they : ''aur ham mein se kisi ke dil mein uskey mutalliq khayal aata hai to Allah tawakkul ke baais usey khatam kar deta hai.'' aur mera khayal hai ke ye jumla ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
4585,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kodhi shakhs ka haath pakda aur usey apney sath hi khaney ke bartan mein rakha aur farmaya : ''Allah par aitimad w bharosa aur tawakkul kartey huey khaao .'' rawahu ibne-Maja .
4586,"Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na ullu manhoos hai aur na koi bimari mutaaddi hai aur na hi koi badshigooni hai. aur agar badshigooni (yani nahusat ( kisi chiz mein hoti to ghar, ghodey aur aurat mein hoti.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4587,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi kaam ke liye nikaltey to aap ya Rashid (raahnumai paney waley) , ya najeeh ( kamiyabi pane-waley (ke alfaz sunna pasand farmaya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4588,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi chiz se badshigooni nahin liya kartey they, jab aap kisi aamil ( governer w hukmran ( ko bhejtey to uska naam daryaft farmatey, agar aap ko uska naam pasand aata to aap us se khush hotey aur us khushi ke aasaar aap ke chehrey par nazar aatey , aur agar aap uska naam napasand kartey to uski naa-pasandeedgi aap ke chehrey par nazar aati. aur jab aap kisi basti mein dakhil hotey to uska naam daryaft farmatey, agar aap ko uska naam achcha lagta to aap khush hotey aur khushi ke aasaar aap ke chehrey par dikhai detey . aur agar uskey naam ko napasand farmatey to nagawari ke asraat aap ke chehrey par numaya hotey . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4589,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham eik ghar mein they jis se hamarey afrad aur amwaal mein izafa hua , phir ham ne wo ghar badal liya to hamarey afrad w amwaal mein kami aa gaee hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us ghar ko chhod do kyonkey ye ghar achcha nahin .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4590,"Hazrat Yahya bin Abdullah bin Buher bayan kartey hain, mujhey us shakhs ne bataya jisney farwa bin Musaik ko bayan kartey huey suna, wo kehtey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey paas Abeen naami zamin hai, hamari kheti w maeeshat (karobar) isi zamin se wabasta hai, lekin wahan ki waba shadeed hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do, kyonkey bimari ke qarib rehna halakat ko dawat dena hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4591,"Hazrat Urwa bin Aamir bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas badshigooni ka zikr kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un mein se behtar chiz nek faal lena hai, aur wo ( badshigooni) kisi musalman ko kaam se mat mana karey, jab tum mein se koi shakhs naa-pasandida chiz dekhey to kahey : aey Allah! tamam bhalaiyan tu hi lata hai aur tamam buraiyan tu hi door karta hai, her qism ke gunah se bachna aur neki karna mehaz teri tofiq se mumkin hai.'' Abu-Dawood ne isey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4592,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kuch aisey batein w maamlat hain jo ham daure-jahiliyat mein kya kartey they, ham kaahinon ke paas jaya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kaahinon ke paas na jaya karo.'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : ham parindon ke zariey faal liya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aisi chiz hai jisey tum mein se koi apney dil mein paata hai wo ( faal lena) tumhen ( kaam karney sey) na rokey .'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : ham mein se kuch aisey hain jo lakeerein khincha kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik Nabi bhi lakeerein khincha kartey they, jis ka khat unke khat ke muwaafiq ho gaya to wo theek hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4593,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaahinon ke barey mein puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''unki koi haisiyat nahin.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kabhi-kabhi wo jo kehtey hain, wesay hi ho jata hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kisi sachi baat ko jin (ooper sey) uchak leta hai to phir wo murghi ki aawaz ki tarah usey apney sathi ke kaan tak pahuncha deta hai, kaahin log is mein so se ziyada jhoot mila detey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4594,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' be-shak farishtey Annaan yani badalon mein utartey hain, aur wo aasman mein honey waley faisla shuda umur (baton) ka tazkira kartey hain to shayatin chori se usey sun letey hain phir wo usey kaahinon tak pahuncha detey hain, aur kaahin uskey sath apni taraf se so jhoot boltey hain.'' Bukhari ."
4595,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi kaahin ke paas ja kar us se kisi gum shuda chiz ke barey mein daryaft karey to us shakhs ki chaalis roz tak Namaz qubul nahin hoti .'' rawahu Muslim ."
4596,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen Hudebiya ke maqam par raat barish ho janey ke baad namaze-Fajr padhaai, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke tumharey rab ne kya farmaya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney farmaya hai : merey bandon mein se baaz ne is haal mein subah ki ke wo mujh par eman laye aur kuchh ne merey sath kufr kiya, jis shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke Fazal aur uski rehmat se ham par barish hui hai to wo mujh par eman laney wala hai aur sitaron ka munkir hai aur raha wo shakhs jisney kaha : falan falan (sitarey ke suqoot) ki wajeh se ham par barish hui hai to wo merey sath kufr karney wala hai aur sitaron par eman rakhney wala hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4597,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah aasman se koi barkat nazil karta hai to logon ka eik giroh uska inkar kar deta hai, Allah barish nazil karta hai lekin wo kehtey hain ke falan falan sitarey ki wajeh se (barish hui) hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4598,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne ilme nujoom hasil kiya to usney jadu ka eik hissey hasil kiya, wo (husool sahar mein) jis qadr badhta gaya usi qadr wo (husool ilme nujum mein) badhta gaya.'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4599,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi kaahin ke paas gaya aur uski baaton ki tasdeeq ki ya usney apni ehaliya se jabkey wo haalate haiz mein ho, jima (sambhog) kiya, ya usney apni ehliya ki pusht mein jima kiya to wo us se bezar hai jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par utaari gaee hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4600,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah aasman par kisi Amr (baat) ka faisla karta hai to farishtey uskey farman se dartey huey apney par hilaatey hain, jaisa ke chattan par zanjeer maarney ki aawaz aati hai, jab unke dilon se khof jata rehta hai to wo kehtey hain, tumharey rab ne kya farmaya hai? wo (muqarrab (qareebi) farishtey) kehtey hain, us zaat ne jo farmaya , wo haq hai, wo buland aur bada hai, chunanche chori se sunney waley is faisley ko sun letey hain, aur chori se sunney waley is tarah eik doosrey ke ooper hotey hain.'' aur Sufiyan (raawi) ne apni hatheli ke zariey uski kaifiyat bayan ki, unhoney us (hatheli) ko khola aur ungliyon ke darmiyan fasla kiya, ''chunanche ooper wala baat sunta hai aur wo is baat ko apney nichey waley ko pahuncha deta hai, phir wo apney se nichey waley tak pahuncha deta hai yahan tak ke (is tarah hotey huey) aakhiri saahir ya kaahin ki zaban tak pahuncha deta hai, aur kabhi-kabhi shetan ke pahunchaney se pehley pehley Shahab saqib usey lag jata hai aur kabhi Shahab saqib ke us tak pahunchney se qabl wo ghaib se dil mein baat dal deta hai aur wo uskey sath sau jhoot mila kar batata hai chunanche kaha jata, kya usney falan waqt is tarah is tarah nahin kaha tha, is kalime ki wajeh sey, jo aasman se suna gaya tha, tasdeeq ho jati hai.'' Bukhari."
4601,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ansaar Sahaba mein se eik sahabi ne mujhey bayan kiya ke is beech mein ke eik raat ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath bethey huey they ke eik sitaara tootaa aur roshan hua. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''jab daure jahiliyat mein is tarah sitaara toot'taa tha to tum kya kaha kartey they?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool hi behtar jantey hain, taaham ye kaha kartey they us raat koi azeem aadmi paida hua hai ya koi azeem aadmi faut hua hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sitaara na kisi ki maut par toot'taa hai aur na kisi ki hayaat par , lekin jab hamara rab , ba-barkat hai naam uska , koi faisla farmata hai to haameleen arsh tasbih bayan kartey hain, baad iske un se qarib aasman waley farishtey Subhanallah kehtey hain yahan tak ke tasbih ki ye aawaz aasmane duniya ke farishton tak pahunch jati hai, phir wo farishtey jo arsh ko uthaney waley farishton ke qarib hotey hain wo haameleen-arsh se kehtey hain, tumharey rab ne kya kaha hai? to wo unhen batatey hain jo Allah Taala ne kaha hota hai, aasman waley eik doosrey se poochhtey hain, yahan tak ke khabar aasmane-duniya tak pahunch jati hai chunanche shayatin is baat ko uchak letey hain, aur wo apney sathiyon ke dil mein ghaib se baat daal detey hain, aur usi doran unhen angaarey maarey jatey hain, jo khabar wo asal shakal mein dilon mein ghaib se baat daal detey hain wo to haq aur durust hoti hai, lekin wo is mein aur mila letey hain, aur izafa kar letey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
4602,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah Taala ne ye sitarey teen maqsadon ke liye paida farmaai hain, unhen aasman ke liye baaise-zeenat banaya , shayatin ke liye maar aur alamat w nishaanaat jinkey zariey rehnumai hasil ki jati hai. jisney unke ilawa kuch aur bayan kya usney ghalati ki, apna hissey ( umr ( zaya kya aur aisi chiz ka takalluf kya jo wo nahin janta . Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey muallaq riwayat kya hai. aur rizeen ki riwayat mein hai, aur usney aisi chiz ka takalluf kya jo na to uskey mutalliq hai aur na usey uska ilm hai aur jiskey ilm se Anbiya (Alaihissalam) aur farishtey bhi aajiz hain. Bukhari w rizeen ."
4603,"Hazrat Rabee se bhi isi tarah marwi (bayan) hai, neez unhoney ye izafa naqal kya hai, Allah ki qism ! Allah ne kisi sitarey mein na to kisi ki zindagi rakhi hai aur na uska rizq rakha hai aur na uski maut rakhi hai, wo to Allah par jhoot baandhtey hain aur sitaron ka faqat bahana banatey hain. rawahu rizeen ."
4604,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ke bayan karda fawaaid ke ilawa ilme-nujoom mein se koi hissey seekha to usney jadu ka eik hissey hasil kya, nujoomi kaahin hai, aur kaahin jadugar hai, aur jadugar kafir hai.'' rawahu rizeen ."
4605,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar Allah paanch saal tak barish rok ley, phir usey barsa dey to logon main eik jamaat kafir ho jaeygi, wo kahengey, ham par majdah sitarey ki wajeh se barish hui hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
